                                           data-track-label="10.1007/s10549-017-4210-z">Adherence to guidelines and breast cancer patients survival: a population-based cohort study analyzed with a causal inference approach
                                        </a>
                                    </h3>
                                    <div class="c-article-meta-recommendations" data-test="recommendation-info">
