substantial contributions to the design and conception of the study. TS and IC took responsibility for the data acquisition of the Madrid sub-cohort; MP-R for the Costa del Sol sub-cohort; and MS, AJ, JL, TD-S, MC, and LD for the Hospital del Mar sub-cohort. PS took responsibility for data analysis, interpretation, and drafting the article. MS, AJ, LD, MC, XC, BI, MR, and IC provided advice for the study design and critical interpretation of the study. All of the authors have read and approved the manuscript.</p><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="corresponding-author">Corresponding author</h3><p id="corresponding-author-list">Correspondence to
                <a id="corresp-c1" aria-label="email Maria Sala" href="mailto:msalaserra@parcdesalutmar.cat">Maria Sala</a>.</p></div></div></section><section data-title="Ethics declarations"><div class="c-article-section" id="ethics-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="ethics">Ethics declarations</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="ethics-content">
              
              
                <h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="FPar1">Conflict of interest</h3>
                <p>The authors have no relevant financial or non-financial interests to disclose. The funding institution took no part in the design, collection, analysis or interpretation of data, drafting, or decision to submit this document for publication.</p>
              
              
                <h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="FPar2">Ethical approval</h3>
                <p>Ethical approval was waived by the Local Ethics Committee of all three institutions in view of the retrospective nature of the study and all the procedures performed were part of routine care.</p>
              
              
                <h3 class="c-article__sub-heading">Informed consent</h3>
                <p>For this type of study, formal consent is not required.</p>
              
            </div></div></section><section data-title="Additional information"><div class="c-article-section" id="additional-information-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="additional-information">Additional information</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="additional-information-content"><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading">Publisher's Note</h3><p>Springer Nature remains neutral with regard to jurisdictional claims in published maps and institutional affiliations.</p></div></div></section><section data-title="Rights and permissions"><div class="c-article-section" id="rightslink-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="rightslink">Rights and permissions</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="rightslink-content">
